# Customer Product EDA Analysis

## Overview

This project performs Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on customer and product datasets using Python.

The goal was to analyze inventory values, product discounts, customer purchasing behavior, and generate business insights.

## Tools Used

- Python
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Jupyter Notebook

## Tasks Performed

- Loaded and explored datasets
- Calculated total inventory value
- Applied product discounts
- Counted total products
- Filtered customers by city and country
- Visualized top purchasing cities
- Analyzed product purchase trends
- Created customer purchase reports
- Identified discounted purchases

## Key Findings

- Total Inventory Value: 13,133,737.88
- Total Products: 100
- Discounted Purchases: 67
- Most Purchased Products:
  - Half
  - Own
  - Every

